---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "YouTube Consulting & Channel Management"
description: "Creator Essentials helps serious creators turn scattered YouTube effort into a clear growth system. Strategy, SEO, audits, coaching, and channel management."
---

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><circle cx="7" cy="7" r="6" stroke="#F21B2D" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="5.5,4.5 10,7 5.5,9.5" fill="#F21B2D"/></svg>
        YouTube-Certified Expert · 123M+ Views
      </div>
      <h1>Stop guessing.<br><em>Start growing.</em></h1>
      <p>Creator Essentials helps serious creators improve their videos, sharpen their channel strategy, and build a repeatable system for growth.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/services/youtube-channel-audit/" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Channel Audit</a>
        <a href="/services/youtube-coaching-program/" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore Coaching</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROOF BAR -->
<section class="bg-cloud" style="padding-block:2.5rem;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="proof-bar" style="justify-content:space-around;">
      <div class="proof-item">
        <strong>123M+</strong>
        <span>Total Views</span>
      </div>
      <div class="proof-item">
        <strong>300K+</strong>
        <span>Subscribers Grown</span>
      </div>
      <div class="proof-item">
        <strong>YouTube</strong>
        <span>Certified Expert</span>
      </div>
      <div class="proof-item">
        <strong>$0</strong>
        <span>Guesswork Required</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">Services</span>
      <h2>What Creator Essentials does for you</h2>
      <p>Each offer has a specific job. Pick the one that fits where you are right now.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card-grid">

      <div class="card card-red">
        <div class="card-number">1</div>
        <h3>Channel Audit</h3>
        <p>100+ points analyzed. Walk away knowing exactly what to fix — SEO, thumbnails, retention, branding, and monetization.</p>
        <a href="/services/youtube-channel-audit/" class="card-cta">
          Get Audited
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M3 7h8M7 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-number">2</div>
        <h3>1-on-1 Coaching</h3>
        <p>$89/month. Daily weekday access to an expert coach. Personalized feedback on titles, thumbnails, and strategy. 7-day free trial.</p>
        <a href="/services/youtube-coaching-program/" class="card-cta">
          Start Free Trial
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M3 7h8M7 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-number">3</div>
        <h3>Channel Management</h3>
        <p>Hand off the day-to-day. SEO, thumbnails, content strategy, analytics reporting — done for you so you can focus on creating.</p>
        <a href="/services/youtube-channel-management/" class="card-cta">
          Learn More
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M3 7h8M7 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-number">4</div>
        <h3>Consulting</h3>
        <p>30–60 minute Zoom sessions starting at $40. Outside perspective on your goals, content gaps, and next steps. No fluff.</p>
        <a href="/services/youtube-consulting/" class="card-cta">
          Book a Session
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M3 7h8M7 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT / ROB -->
<section class="bg-cloud">
  <div class="container" style="display:grid; gap:3rem; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; align-items:center;">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">About Rob</span>
      <h2>I've been exactly where you are.</h2>
      <p>Hi, I'm Rob — founder of Creator Essentials and a former full-time content creator. I know what it feels like to be directionless, scared of the camera, and stuck in analysis paralysis.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">Years later, I've grown channels to over 123 million views and 300,000 subscribers. I'm YouTube-certified, and I've helped creators at every level build systems that actually work.</p>
      <a href="/about/" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">More About Me</a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="card" style="background:var(--charcoal); border-color:transparent;">
        <blockquote style="color:var(--white); font-size:1.1rem; font-family:var(--font-head); line-height:1.4; margin-bottom:1rem;">"Creator growth without the guesswork."</blockquote>
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size:0.875rem; margin:0;">Channels worked with: @LaserAway · @DanHenry · @premiermarbleracing</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">The Process</span>
      <h2>From guessing to a clear plan in four steps</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="steps" style="max-width:560px;">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Book or reach out</h4>
          <p>Choose a service and share your channel details. No long intake forms.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Channel analysis</h4>
          <p>Rob reviews your channel before you speak — so the session is focused on your specific bottlenecks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Clear action items</h4>
          <p>Walk away with a prioritized list of what to fix, improve, or stop doing entirely.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Implement and grow</h4>
          <p>Apply the recommendations. Ongoing coaching or management available to keep the momentum going.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
<section class="bg-cloud">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">What people say</span>
      <h2>Creators who stopped guessing</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="testimonial">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <blockquote>"Great in-depth feedback. Helped me with a lot of more advanced SEO details of my channel that I wouldn't have found on my own."</blockquote>
        <div class="testimonial-source">Verified Client</div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <blockquote>"I can highly recommend it. My YouTube channel was reviewed in a professional way and I received a full report with clear next steps."</blockquote>
        <div class="testimonial-source">Verified Client</div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <blockquote>"Fantastic service! Finally got the outside perspective I needed. Knew what to work on the same day."</blockquote>
        <div class="testimonial-source">Verified Client</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- RECENT BLOG POSTS -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">From the blog</span>
      <h2>Free creator strategy resources</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="card-grid">
      {% for post in collections.posts | slice(0, 3) %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-card" style="text-decoration:none; color:inherit;">
        <div class="post-card-meta">
          <time datetime="{{ post.date | dateISO }}">{{ post.date | dateDisplay }}</time>
          {% if post.data.tags %} · <span class="post-tag">{{ post.data.tags[0] }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <span class="card-cta">
          Read more
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M3 7h8M7 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:2rem;">
      <a href="/blog/" class="btn btn-secondary">View All Articles</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA BANNER -->
<section class="bg-charcoal cta-banner">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--red);">Ready to grow?</span>
    <h2>Get Started Today</h2>
    <p>You deserve to feel good about your YouTube channel. Reach out and I'll put a plan together.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="/services/youtube-channel-audit/" class="btn btn-white">Get a Channel Audit</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline-white">Contact Me</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
